bility to prioritize work, adapt to changing workloads with excellent organizational skills Ability to work independently The Saskatchewan Health Authority offers competitive salaries and a comprehensive benefits package. Those who thrive working in a fast-paced, stimulating environment will be interested in joining our team. Interested applicants are invited to submit a cover letter, resume and three references in confidence, quoting Job Number RQ-00007103, by August 31, 2023 to: Email: jobs@rqhealth.ca Employment Services Saskatchewan Health Authority 2180 23rd Ave. Regina, SKS4S 0A5 Applicants considered for interviews will be contacted. www.saskhealthauthority.ca https://saskhealthauthority.libguides.com/home Compensation Rate of Pay: 22.60 - 24.21 Closes: 31 August, 2023 Saskatchewan Health Authority Library Regina , SK Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
