mation, or to apply for the position, please go to: https://jobs.novascotia.ca/job/HALIFAX-Collections-Access-Lead-Librarian-3-NS-B3H-1W4/572414117/ Compensation $2,543.38 - $3,091.70 Bi-Weekly (PR13) Closes: 4 August, 2023 Nova Scotia Provincial Library Halifax , NS Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
